WEBVTT

00:00:27.760 --> 00:00:28.920
Wei.

00:00:46.920 --> 00:00:48.920
But you shouldn't take me for a fool.

00:00:49.800 --> 00:00:51.880
Wei Cheng controls the Jingzhao Prefecture.

00:00:51.880 --> 00:00:53.140
Here in Chang'an City,

00:00:53.400 --> 00:00:56.960
he and I, Chen Jingbian, each rule our own domain.

00:00:57.720 --> 00:01:00.380
He's also notoriously cowardly and lecherous.

00:01:01.440 --> 00:01:02.900
You, as a handsome doctor,

00:01:03.240 --> 00:01:04.959
well-versed in the art of health preservation,

00:01:04.959 --> 00:01:06.040
must know

00:01:06.960 --> 00:01:09.800
why Prefect Wei invited you for tea.

00:01:14.080 --> 00:01:16.000
All that talk about living in chaotic times.

00:01:16.000 --> 00:01:18.130
Claiming you only sought protection.

00:01:18.600 --> 00:01:19.600
And that Wei Cheng

00:01:20.520 --> 00:01:21.960
was your best option.

00:01:23.200 --> 00:01:23.840
Yet you

00:01:25.160 --> 00:01:26.600
schemed elaborately

00:01:27.360 --> 00:01:28.690
and plotted carefully,

00:01:28.920 --> 00:01:31.680
risking everything to get close to me.

00:01:32.520 --> 00:01:34.200
How can I trust you?

00:01:47.960 --> 00:01:50.720
I won't hold your previous words against you.

00:01:52.759 --> 00:01:54.600
I'll give you one last chance

00:01:54.880 --> 00:01:57.120
to tell me the truth.

00:02:03.360 --> 00:02:04.040
Lord Chen,

00:02:05.040 --> 00:02:07.640
please help this humble servant seek justice!

00:02:11.000 --> 00:02:13.040
My family has practiced medicine for generations.

00:02:13.040 --> 00:02:15.640
My father was especially skilled in medicine.

00:02:16.040 --> 00:02:19.570
Thirteen years ago, he happened to save an imperial inspector.

00:02:20.160 --> 00:02:23.290
But that dog of an official coveted our family's wealth.

00:02:23.480 --> 00:02:26.400
After recovering, he brought men to murder my entire family.

00:02:26.400 --> 00:02:29.160
I was fortunate to escape by playing dead.

00:02:30.400 --> 00:02:33.520
But my father, mother, and little brother

00:02:34.200 --> 00:02:36.000
were all brutally slaughtered.

00:02:37.200 --> 00:02:38.860
I made inquiries everywhere.

00:02:38.880 --> 00:02:40.920
Finally, heaven rewarded my persistence

00:02:40.920 --> 00:02:41.850
and I discovered

00:02:42.120 --> 00:02:43.960
that the scoundrel had transformed himself

00:02:43.960 --> 00:02:45.960
into the Prefect of Chang'an City.

00:02:49.400 --> 00:02:51.730
I went to great lengths to come to your side

00:02:51.760 --> 00:02:53.600
just to earn your trust.

00:02:54.440 --> 00:02:55.640
Help me kill Wei Cheng

00:02:56.120 --> 00:02:57.320
and avenge my family.

00:03:05.240 --> 00:03:06.400
So you're telling me

00:03:07.320 --> 00:03:09.160
that everything you told me before

00:03:09.160 --> 00:03:10.240
was a lie.

00:03:11.320 --> 00:03:15.200
Do you know the price

00:03:15.840 --> 00:03:17.300
for not telling the truth?

00:03:20.560 --> 00:03:21.120
Li Ling.

00:03:22.240 --> 00:03:22.770
Yes, sir.

00:03:23.120 --> 00:03:24.120
Give me the knife.

00:03:27.000 --> 00:03:27.530
Sir Chen,

00:03:27.800 --> 00:03:28.860
