00:03:43.000 --> 00:03:46.079
Let me see how determined you really are.

00:04:13.000 --> 00:04:14.860
My worthless life means nothing.

00:04:15.520 --> 00:04:18.040
Please, Master Chen, avenge my family.

00:04:24.240 --> 00:04:24.760
Li Ling!

00:04:25.600 --> 00:04:26.660
What are you doing?

00:04:27.200 --> 00:04:28.400
In response to you, sir,

00:04:28.400 --> 00:04:29.730
