00:05:52.480 --> 00:05:53.080
Father.

00:05:53.760 --> 00:05:54.280
Mother.

00:05:55.120 --> 00:05:55.780
Xiaochuan.

00:05:56.920 --> 00:05:57.920
It's coming soon.

00:05:58.760 --> 00:06:00.480
The day I avenge you

00:06:01.480 --> 00:06:02.520
is not far away.

00:06:05.200 --> 00:06:05.660
Mother.

00:06:08.600 --> 00:06:09.040
Xiaochuan.

00:06:09.040 --> 00:06:09.800
Xiaochuan.

00:06:19.720 --> 00:06:21.380
Miss Nongyu, this way please.

00:06:29.560 --> 00:06:31.220
The master is waiting for you.

00:06:37.720 --> 00:06:38.560
I, Nongyu,

00:06:38.840 --> 00:06:40.880
thank you for your protection, Lord Chen.

00:06:40.880 --> 00:06:41.640
Here I am.

00:06:43.440 --> 00:06:46.280
Have you met all these ladies?

00:06:49.720 --> 00:06:51.520
To welcome you to our household,

00:06:51.840 --> 00:06:53.840
I've called them all here.

00:06:55.880 --> 00:06:56.800
Nongyu,

00:06:58.120 --> 00:07:00.360
From now on, in this room,

00:07:00.880 --> 00:07:02.680
you'll have your own place.

00:07:04.080 --> 00:07:07.520
But whether you can please our family in the future,

00:07:08.520 --> 00:07:10.520
depends on your skills and talents.

00:07:12.280 --> 00:07:13.520
I'm just a healer,

00:07:13.720 --> 00:07:16.280
how could I compare myself to these ladies?

00:07:20.800 --> 00:07:22.120
Whether it's treating patients

00:07:22.120 --> 00:07:23.200
or serving tea,

00:07:24.200 --> 00:07:25.400
Just look at them.

00:07:26.000 --> 00:07:28.520
Which one of them doesn't follow orders?

00:07:29.280 --> 00:07:30.200
Or perhaps

00:07:31.360 --> 00:07:34.800
you think you're better than them?

00:07:35.560 --> 00:07:36.490
I wouldn't dare.

00:07:38.600 --> 00:07:39.440
Shiyuan.

00:07:44.400 --> 00:07:45.000
Father.

00:07:45.520 --> 00:07:48.580
From now on, you two will address each other as sisters.

00:07:49.480 --> 00:07:53.280
You'll be responsible for all arrangements for Nongyu's entry into the household.

00:07:53.280 --> 00:07:54.480
Don't worry, Father.

00:07:55.040 --> 00:07:57.000
I'll make sure she falls in line.

00:08:03.800 --> 00:08:05.560
May I ask how old you are?

00:08:06.400 --> 00:08:09.130
Should I call you elder sister or younger sister?

00:08:10.400 --> 00:08:11.240
I'm new here.

00:08:11.640 --> 00:08:13.640
How could I presume to be your elder?

00:08:15.520 --> 00:08:16.400
Follow me.

00:08:17.520 --> 00:08:19.520
What's meant to happen will happen.

00:08:20.440 --> 00:08:25.720
Besides, isn't it better to have one more sister?

00:08:28.720 --> 00:08:29.640
Father,

00:08:30.320 --> 00:08:32.120
are you disappointed in me?

00:08:34.760 --> 00:08:38.720
How could a father ever be disappointed in his daughter?

00:08:40.480 --> 00:08:41.960
My dear girl.

00:08:43.480 --> 00:08:46.440
I care about you more than anything.

00:08:48.160 --> 00:08:49.760
Look around this household.

00:08:50.040 --> 00:08:51.360
Who else is like you?

00:08:52.400 --> 00:08:54.200
You're my confidant.

00:08:57.480 --> 00:09:00.720
You are my eyes in this household.

00:09:02.080 --> 00:09:05.600
If that Nongyu dares to cause any trouble,

00:09:06.560 --> 00:09:07.800
don't take her life,

00:09:08.640 --> 00:09:09.770
just break her legs.

00:09:10.280 --> 00:09:12.800
Otherwise she'll think my household

00:09:13.120 --> 00:09:14.680
is a place where she can come

00:09:15.320 --> 00:09:16.720
and go as she pleases.

00:09:26.480 --> 00:09:28.560
From today on, you'll be living here.

00:09:29.120 --> 00:09:30.880
All food, drink and expenses here

00:09:30.880 --> 00:09:32.280
will be under my control.

00:09:33.680 --> 00:09:36.320
Every morning, you must come to my courtyard to pay respects.

00:09:36.320 --> 00:09:37.560
Whatever you said,

00:09:37.560 --> 00:09:38.280
