00:09:38.280 --> 00:09:39.160
whoever you met the day before,

00:09:39.160 --> 00:09:41.360
you must report it all to me truthfully.

00:09:41.600 --> 00:09:42.280
Also,

00:09:42.760 --> 00:09:44.090
without my permission,

00:09:44.840 --> 00:09:47.680
you are not allowed to step foot outside the Chen residence.

00:09:47.680 --> 00:09:48.740
Do you understand?

00:10:04.120 --> 00:10:05.800
