00:10:26.000 --> 00:10:26.730
How dare you!

00:10:27.680 --> 00:10:30.610
I fear you haven't recovered well after childbirth.

00:10:31.320 --> 00:10:32.250
What did you say?

00:10:32.400 --> 00:10:34.000
When have I ever given birth?

00:10:36.560 --> 00:10:38.320
Don't forget what I do for a living.

00:10:38.320 --> 00:10:40.720
Of course I know you've given birth before.

00:10:40.720 --> 00:10:41.320
Besides,

00:10:41.840 --> 00:10:44.600
I can tell when you gave birth, the baby's gender, if you had enough milk,

00:10:44.600 --> 00:10:46.160
and whether you suffered from postpartum depression.

00:10:46.160 --> 00:10:47.360
